    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/98575fb5fdded47753f2e01ef31b4933.poster.avif?t=1727868949\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/98575fb5fdded47753f2e01ef31b4933.webm?t=1727868949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/98575fb5fdded47753f2e01ef31b4933.mp4?t=1727868949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《巨塔57》 故事概要</strong></h2>在这个柴油朋克风格的反乌托邦世界中，伫立着许多“巨塔”，它们是人类文明仅存的聚集地。一小队神通广大之人受命潜入其中离群索居的57号巨塔。而他们各自的技能，武器和团队合作能力将决定其接下来的命运。<br><br>《巨塔57》是一款像素风格的双轴射击游戏，有着高度可破坏的场景，且非常注重团队合作。同时也是为了找回当年像素游戏感觉的一次全新尝试。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《巨塔57》的媒体评价</strong></h2><i>“（······）画面风格超赞，玩法动感十足且氛围很酷。”</i><br><strong>—— Hardcore Gamer</strong><br><br><i>“制作人当时跟我讲：‘行了，现在你得走去那儿买双新腿，’我的好感度一下就满了，有时入坑靠的就是这种细节。<br>（······）《巨塔57》将会是一款看重玩家合作的独立佳作。”</i><br><strong>—— WorthPlaying</strong><br><br><i>“《巨塔57》是个有趣又奇葩的射击游戏，里面真是各种混乱，甚至还有个装着机械义肢的林肯在大杀四方，想想看没有机械腿林肯的弹幕游戏还算什么弹幕游戏？”</i><br><strong>—— PlayStation LifeStyle</strong><br><br><i>“（······）这是我最期盼的游戏之一，而且它在Kickstarter和绿光上都大获成功。”</i><br><strong>—— IndieRetroNews</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特性：</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >街机玩法，爽快紧凑</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/1af402f1eb0728d365c81bb566058ff7.poster.avif?t=1727868949\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/1af402f1eb0728d365c81bb566058ff7.webm?t=1727868949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/1af402f1eb0728d365c81bb566058ff7.mp4?t=1727868949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>玩法复制不如风格复古。拿好武器大杀四方，只要你别死就成。《巨塔57》用极简的游戏规则构建出了丰富的情景，同时走的还是硬派路子。例如只有一条命且复活次数有限，而且在毫无准备的时候就会难度陡增。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >行家里手，任君选择</h2> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/e98c0af0869a673d0084407d9c36e063.poster.avif?t=1727868949\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/e98c0af0869a673d0084407d9c36e063.webm?t=1727868949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/e98c0af0869a673d0084407d9c36e063.mp4?t=1727868949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏中的6个角色各自都有着独特的技能，以及可升级的武器和道具。有时候你的角色可能在任务中会不幸缺根胳膊少条腿，千万别担心 - 你能换个更好的！精通了这些组合之后，登顶巨塔57之路将充满乐趣。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >并肩协作，大杀四方</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/1279b663463c64f5b90909b1b28c1685.poster.avif?t=1727868949\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/1279b663463c64f5b90909b1b28c1685.webm?t=1727868949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/1279b663463c64f5b90909b1b28c1685.mp4?t=1727868949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>跟朋友一起疯才是真爽。《巨塔57》的主线兼顾了单人模式和本地/在线联机。不管是包抄，埋伏，协力攻击甚至是集火攻击，想怎么爽就怎么来！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >柴油朋克，前所未见</h2> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/09062876b529dbdf17d72f2216ecaf3e.poster.avif?t=1727868949\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/09062876b529dbdf17d72f2216ecaf3e.webm?t=1727868949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/09062876b529dbdf17d72f2216ecaf3e.mp4?t=1727868949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>这个世界是由地面、电梯、商铺、终端机、暗门还有不为人知的秘密小径一起构建出的一座巨塔迷宫。随机生成的关卡什么的自然是不存在的 - 要知道《巨塔57》里所有东西可都是以像素级的最高水准精心打造。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拆砖卸瓦，不在话下</h2> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/9585d2a16bb9f50718fd9145e0af07e7.poster.avif?t=1727868949\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/9585d2a16bb9f50718fd9145e0af07e7.webm?t=1727868949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/9585d2a16bb9f50718fd9145e0af07e7.mp4?t=1727868949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>打碎，砸坏或是射爆都行。重新装弹！再来一轮！有谁会不喜欢东西被炸烂呢？看吶 - 满目的残垣断壁和血淋林的脚印 - 这可都是你在巨塔中杀出血路的最佳佐证。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >胆大心细，巧妙克敌</h2> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/6bcb8a617724d8a5518d5be5aebefe87.poster.avif?t=1727868949\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/6bcb8a617724d8a5518d5be5aebefe87.webm?t=1727868949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530950/extras/6bcb8a617724d8a5518d5be5aebefe87.mp4?t=1727868949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>每个敌人都有独特的生成机制，移动以及攻击模式，当然还有各自的弱点。如果你不想被秒的话，还是早点弄清楚它们的弱点吧。",
